    "description": "Bang Bang Pull Pull is the most literal on-rail shooter of them all!<br>In the game, you do bang bang to anything that moves and pull everything of value, all while riding a fast-moving mining cart through various handcrafted levels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040130/extras/7f99f8e41812f6498e826204ff7748de.poster.avif?t=1720529603\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040130/extras/7f99f8e41812f6498e826204ff7748de.webm?t=1720529603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040130/extras/7f99f8e41812f6498e826204ff7748de.mp4?t=1720529603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Let us introduce you to a Gun, your first new friend who will accompany you on this wild journey. Forget about magazine size and reloads. Who has time for that? Just shoot and then shoot more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040130/extras/98f6fa396c624a9ced9f9519344fc05e.poster.avif?t=1720529603\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040130/extras/98f6fa396c624a9ced9f9519344fc05e.webm?t=1720529603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040130/extras/98f6fa396c624a9ced9f9519344fc05e.mp4?t=1720529603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Lasso will be your right-hand man. There’s no time to stop and loot. Just grab and pull everything you want while riding through the level at top speed!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040130/extras/14eb5b263db659d2f5a983396c8bd52d.poster.avif?t=1720529603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040130/extras/14eb5b263db659d2f5a983396c8bd52d.webm?t=1720529603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040130/extras/14eb5b263db659d2f5a983396c8bd52d.mp4?t=1720529603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore different routes, discover secrets, and have fun. The ride is short, fast, packed, and lean. Easy to grab, easy to try, and always just a button press away from another run!<br><br>Enjoy handcrafted and tightly intertwined levels with over-the-top themes and badass music to accompany you on your wacky adventures and crazy stunts.",
